🇮🇳 Indian Army – Class 10 Computer Project

Created by: Shreyansh Gupta

This is a school-level web project created using HTML and CSS, developed as part of the Class 10 Computer Applications curriculum. The project is a tribute to the Indian Army, showcasing its strength, divisions, and achievements through a clean and informative website design.

🌟 Features:

Static website built using pure HTML and CSS

Responsive and visually appealing layout

Informative sections about the Indian Army's structure, history, and key facts

Simple navigation and user-friendly interface

Educational purpose with patriotic theme

🛠️ Technologies Used:

HTML5

CSS3

🎯 Project Goal:

To demonstrate basic web development skills while creating an educational website that honors the Indian Army and spreads awareness among students and viewers.
